data.description: Home sits on a water way that leads to Cross Lake with excellent white perch fishing from the bank of the property. Extra living area by the bedrooms and could be a 4th bedroom. Fresh paint, some new ceramic flooring, new Quartz counter top on kitchen island. Corien counter tops in kitchen as well. Large primary bedroom with 2 walk in closets. There is a gate at the driveway entrance for extra security. Large screened in patio. Nice property. No city taxes. Roof was replaced in 2021. Nice shed out back.
